HEADWORD: Ungenerous
<hw>Un*gen"er*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not generous;
illiberal; ignoble; unkind; dishonorable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The victor never will impose on Cato⟦br⟧
<qex>Ungenerous</qex> terms.</q> <rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

